es Sodemanns gate uoffisielt Leistad-gata, etter familien Leistad som bebodde flere hus i str\u00f8ket.", "Jacob Hersleb Sodemann 1780-1849"]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|trondheim"}, {"field": "category2", "value": "nyheter|trondheim|byens gater"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "9e843b9a82d8f4a9b49fc2acd41e96743ca4c1bb805deab24410eae7620c60c5"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-04-30T23:24:30.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Sodemanns gate ligger p\u00e5 Lademoen og g\u00e5r fra Strandveien til General von Kroghs gate."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1104421.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/ver2%20Sodemanns"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/15cceabb2358ade71867d647adcb2dde1989dc43.jpg?598227d3"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "Sodemanns gate -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "15cceabb2358ade71867d647adcb2dde1989dc43"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "byens gater", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "arts-and-entertainment"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["svensk", "norsk", "gate"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["realskolen", "trondhjems", "norges", "lademoen", "riksdag", "sveriges", "general von kroghs", "realskole", "leistad", "sodemann", "storting", "strandveien", "sparbu"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["aure", "vasa", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["sara rebekka hersleb", "lorentz holst sodemann", "jacob hersleb sodemann", "anne ly